                    hereinafter called as the "<strong>OWNER</strong>" (which expression shall, wherever the context so requires, be deemed to mean and include his heirs, legal representatives, administrators and <span class="noalign">assigns);</span><br/>
                    <br/>
                    <span class="noalign">(ii) M/s Vajram Estates Private Limited<br/>
